{"tid":424043,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯]睇完港大同中大 cheer 我正式宣布中大成為新香港一大","createTime":"2017-10-04T11:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T16:56:07.000Z","uid":103616,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f3ea664824ebb3f8db8264f50f2150b7c60830","tid":424043,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 &quot;一大&quot;HKU啲cheer竟然係小學雞口號<br />\n乜撚野無臭狐 乜撚野幾時入宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲細咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncheer緊係CU嘅威水好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLlJqKxJnWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNLlJqKxJnWA&d=frl0UrnvNjjxBuJ1bdA3spWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ac9e7ad2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLlJqKxJnWA</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「鍾意北上去dup骨 搞到全身生粒粒」</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「無波仲着小背心」</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「汁多肉厚好騎呢」</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「XX女仔扮密實，西門大開任進入」 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「崇基女宿係妓寨，鍾意SM好變態」<br />\n「組仔叫雞唔俾錢，組女做雞好淫賤」<br />\n「聯合組媽最盡責﹐含吹舐啜有方法﹐皆因家法好嚴格」<br />\n「崇基啲女好淫賤，晚晚都要玩坐蓮，重要棍上舞翩翩，苦練冰火五重天」 <br />\n「崇基啲仔係舞男，被女搞到生晒癌，個個切晒做太監，入宮等新亞嚟探」 <br />\n「逸夫起頭真係難，冇錢冇面人又煩，駐紮邊疆似嚿飯，調理農務杏加橙」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來CU學生個個臥底藏龍 真係好型好有威力啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對比起 HKU根本就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以我而家正式宣布中大成為新香港一大 不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"32c75d1703e53a5a77ce70b25e3492534d5bf6f0","tid":424043,"uid":150611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a504d3a1d33842dbd57c74d6180edd7df3bd5306","tid":424043,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"HKU學生一定係讀書讀到傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔識享受<br />\n鹹帶都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日日掛住煲粥煮糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHKU學生係咪性冷感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中大就唔同喇<br />\n成日北上dup骨 又識玩SM<br />\n女同學成日做雞 男同學仲要係舞男<br />\n人生經驗擺明俾垃圾HKU仔豐富<br />\n中大唔做一大仲等邊個做？</span></span>"},{"pid":"1eddbd90ec58470a10cbb48a0464287575d93819","tid":424043,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"好想俾聯合組媽瘋狂含吹舐啜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下年一定要入中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ab1a2170433c77095581474ff5bb2199d79431","tid":424043,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"HKU班垃圾死曬去邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a063ac032e44cd548cdb803b8bcdc2da6c8703","tid":424043,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"咁計能大仲唔係一大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，冇Hall冇beat"},{"pid":"c810328c0bad5dc3db71d4c6e581dd0ed3feda91","t